research_municipality_step.notes: Edinburg, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. Omar Ochoa was sworn in as Mayor following the November 2025 election. Ramiro Garza Jr. was the previous mayor. A runoff election for Council Member Place 2 between Jason De Leon and Moises Segovia was slated for December 2025. However, current information from late 2024 lists Jason De Leon as a council member. The other council members are listed as per recent information.
